<CATEGORY> usa </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> NYC Shuts Times Square Sex Shop </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- The hardiest and most infamous of Times Square's  
sex shops has been shut down by the city. 
</P>
<P>
	Authorities closed down Show World on Thursday, saying it housed  
a fencing operation dealing in expensive electronic equipment. 
</P>
<P>
	Show World offers video peep shows and sells X-rated videos.  
</P>
<P>
	The shop's lawyer said the alleged fencing ring involved one man  
who was leasing space from Show World. 
</P>
<P>
	``The city took this isolated incident and capitalized, closing  
it this way when they couldn't close it legitimately,'' Herald 
Price Fahringer said. 
</P>
<P>
	He said he will go to court Wednesday to contest the closing:  
``We have every expectation that we'll be able to reopen.'' 
</P>
<P>
	The city arrested eight suspects in the fencing operation and  
shut Show World down under its ordinance against nuisances. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
