	Fernandez Beats Serena Williams  
</P>
<P>
	PARIS (AP) -- Mary Joe Fernandez beat Serena Williams 6-3, 1-6,  
6-0 today, knocking Serena out from a possible French Open 
semifinal clash with sister Venus. Andre Agassi scored a 6-4, 6-4, 
6-3 win over Chris Woodruff to reach the round of 16 and a probable 
matchup with defending champion Carlos Moya. Patrick Rafter 
advanced to the third round with a 7-5, 6-0, 2-6, 6-4 victory 
against clay-court specialist Nicolas Escude of France. 

</P>
<P>
	AP NewsBrief by DAVID GOODMAN  
