longer traded separately, though they remain in use. Based on euro 
rates, the dollar is worth: 1.8675 German marks, down from 1.8705; 
6.2633 French francs, down from 6.2735; 2.1042 Dutch guilders, down 
from 2.1076; and 1,848.82 Italian lire, down from 1,851.83 
</P>
