<HEADLINE> Sabres' Hasek Ready for Game 4 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	BUFFALO, N.Y. (AP) -- Dominik Hasek skated briefly on Friday,  
performed a few pirouettes and other assorted goalie maneuvers, 
then uttered some words the Toronto Maple Leafs didn't necessarily 
want to hear. 
